#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Random_Number_Generation/rand.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Random_Number_Generation/rand.md:4
msgid ""
"简介：给定 1 个 seed 标量和 1 个 offset 块，返回 1 个 在 **U**(**0**,**1**) 中的 float32 类型的随机块。\n"
"原型：\n"
msgstr ""
"**Description:** Given a seed scalar and an offset block, returns a random block of type float32 in **U**(**0**,**1**).  \n"
"**Prototype:**\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Random_Number_Generation/rand.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.rand(\n"
" seed,\n"
" offset,\n"
" n_rounds: constexpr = 10\n"
")\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Random_Number_Generation/rand.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Random_Number_Generation/rand.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Random_Number_Generation/rand.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `seed`        | `int`或 `tensor`           | 用于生成随机数的种子                                                   |\n"
"| `offset`       |`int`或 `tensor`     | 用于生成随机数的偏移量                     |\n"
"| `n_rounds`     | `constexpr`，默认值为10   | Philox 算法的迭代轮数 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `seed`        | `int` or `tensor` | Seed used to generate random numbers |\n"
"| `offset`      | `int` or `tensor` | Offset used to generate random numbers |\n"
"| `n_rounds`    | `constexpr`, default value is 10 | Number of rounds for the Philox algorithm |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Random_Number_Generation/rand.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"1 个 float32 类型的随机块，其shape与offset的shape相同，其值在 `[0.0, 1.0)` 区间内均匀分布\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"A random block of type `float32`, with the same shape as `offset`, and values uniformly distributed in the interval `[0.0, 1.0)`.\n"

